# Pin line endings for files where mismatch would silently desync the
# wire-cache hash check (build_wires.py vs. browser fetch). The hash itself
# is now byte-mode safe, but keeping the working tree LF avoids noisy diffs
# across machines with different core.autocrlf settings.
public/board.svg          text eol=lf
public/board.wires.json   text eol=lf
